<paragraph id="5F0D7A74E92B658AFE8135EF7A02AA8F" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">Type.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="A671CCE6E0483108687357C9C1FAFB56" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">
BOLIVIA. Santa Cruz, Prov. Cordillera, Pie de la Muela del Diablo, Boyuibe-Camiri, 
<emphasis id="5B871D52D37AC651D880D22FB0127CD2" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">J.R.I. Wood, D. Villarroel &amp; B. Williams</emphasis>
